  "body": "`Version      : 1.10.67-0-cff76f48d-20210513`\r\n\r\nRepro:\r\n```\r\ncurl -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionByHash\",\"params\":[\"0xc7a20d6fc41b358c2039f0b0aa0b650d2a5876d82960a45a6a18eb84e13fde6b\"]}'\r\n```\r\n\r\n`\"v\": \"0x1b\"` this is wrong, should be `\"v\": \"0x0\"`\r\n\r\n`chainId` property is missing entirely.\r\n\r\nAlso, `type` field in a legacy transaction is `0x00` but every other client just returns `0x0`",
